<mediaPoint id="fig01_10" type="IMG" mediaType="TID1" mediaSize="3" order="12" href="chap01.html#fig01_10"><desc><![CDATA[<b>Figure 1-10</b> Extraocular muscles, frontal view, left eye, with globe removed. <span style="font-size:0.8em"><i>(Reproduced with permission from Dutton JJ.</i> Atlas of Clinical and Surgical Orbital Anatomy. <i>Philadelphia: Saunders; 1994.)</i></span>]]></desc><mediaPath src="images/img_p14-1.jpg" thumbSrc="images/img_p14-1.jpg"/></mediaPoint>
