<mediaPoint id="fig02_21" type="IMG" mediaType="TID1" mediaSize="3" order="63" href="chap02.html#fig02_21"><desc><![CDATA[<b>Figure 2-21</b> Retinal pigment epithelium and the Bruch membrane. <span style="font-size:0.8em"><i>(Illustration by Thomas A. Weingeist, PhD, MD.)</i></span>]]></desc><mediaPath src="images/img_p61-1.jpg" thumbSrc="images/img_p61-1.jpg"/></mediaPoint>
