<mediaMap>
<mediaPoint id="fig02_26" type="IMG" mediaType="TID1" mediaSize="3" order="68" href="chap02.html#fig02_26"><desc><![CDATA[<b>Figure 2-26</b> <b>A</b> and <b>B,</b> Scanning electron micrographs of the relationship between lens fiber packing and interdigitation <i>(arrows in B)</i>. <span style="font-size:0.8em"><i>(Reproduced with permission from Kessel RG, Kardon RH.</i> Tissues and Organs: A Text-Atlas of Scanning Electron Microscopy. <i>San Francisco: WH Freeman; 1979.)</i></span>]]></desc><mediaPath src="images/img_p66ab.jpg" thumbSrc="images/img_p66ab.jpg"/></mediaPoint>
