<mediaPoint id="fig02_27" type="IMG" mediaType="TID1" mediaSize="3" order="69" href="chap02.html#fig02_27"><desc><![CDATA[<b>Figure 2-27</b> Regional differences in the retina. <b>A,</b> Papillomacular bundle. <b>B,</b> Macula. <b>C,</b> Peripheral retina. (H&#x0026;E, all same magnification.) <span style="font-size:0.8em"><i>(Courtesy of Thomas A. Weingeist, PhD, MD.)</i></span>]]></desc><mediaPath src="images/img_p68abc.jpg" thumbSrc="images/img_p68abc.jpg"/></mediaPoint>
