<mediaMap>
<mediaPoint id="fig07_5" type="IMG" mediaType="TID1" mediaSize="3" order="148" href="chap07.html#fig07_5"><desc><![CDATA[<b>Figure 7-5</b> Inflammatory mediators in keratoconjunctivitis sicca. MMPs = matrix metalloproteinases. <span style="font-size:0.8em"><i>(Reproduced with permission from Pflugfelder SC. Antiinflammatory therapy for dry eye.</i> Am J Ophthalmol. <i>2004;137(2):338.)</i></span>]]></desc><mediaPath src="images/img_p221-1.jpg" thumbSrc="images/img_p221-1.jpg"/></mediaPoint>
