<mediaPoint id="fig10_1" type="IMG" mediaType="TID1" mediaSize="3" order="153" href="chap10.html#fig10_1"><desc><![CDATA[<b>Figure 10-1</b> The mammalian lens in schematic cross section. The <i>small arrowheads</i> indicate the direction of cell migration from the epithelium to the cortex. <span style="font-size:0.8em"><i>(Reproduced with permission from Anderson RE, ed.</i> Biochemistry of the Eye. <i>San Francisco: American Academy of Ophthalmology; 1983:112.)</i></span>]]></desc><mediaPath src="images/img_p242.jpg" thumbSrc="images/img_p242.jpg"/></mediaPoint>
